              "body": "![medium](https://www.gstatic.com/codereviewagent/medium-priority.svg)\n\nThe access log schema in the plan is missing the `skill_context` field required by R13 in the brainstorm. This field is important for auditing which skill triggered the vault access and should be included in the implementation unit.\n\n```suggestion\n  - store `{timestamp, command, query_hash, query_len, pages_returned, bytes_returned, exit_code, skill_context?}`\n```",
