              "author": {
                "login": "chatgpt-codex-connector"
              },
              "body": "**<sub><sub>![P2 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P2-yellow?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Allow `cairn get` to serve curated root docs**\n\nUnit 2 defines `get <page>` as reading only `<vault>/wiki/<page>.md`, but R7 requires lazy mode to fetch full `context.md` via `cairn get context`. If implemented as written, `context.md` becomes unreachable through the sanctioned API after eager injection is removed, causing a behavior regression or pushing agents back toward direct file reads. The `get` contract should include curated root files (at least `context.md`) or the requirement should be revised.\n\nUseful? React with 👍 / 👎.",
